        meta(name="description" content="INFRA INDIA MART Supplies Ordinary Portland cement - OPC 53 Grade & OPC 43 Grade, Portland pozzolana cement- PPC Cement, Sulphates resisting cement – SRPC cement, Blast Furnace Slag Cement – PSC Slag Cement")
        meta(name="description" content="At INFRA INDIA MART, our focus extends far beyond mere cement supply; we prioritize forging enduring relationships with our customers built on trust and respect. Our relentless dedication to customer satisfaction has solidified our position as a premier supplier in the cement market. Backed by a robust support team,  With a team characterized by passion and dedication, INFRA INDIA MART is primed for sustained growth and success. Our unwavering pursuit of excellence ensures that we remain at the forefront of the industry as a leading cement supplier, earning the trust and loyalty of customers nationwide.")
